milestones.description: Tim de Leede has broken the record for most ducks (4) in ODIs for NED, going past Esmeijer's 3
van Troost has broken the record for most ODIs (9) as captain for NED, going past Lefebvre
This is the lowest match aggregate (185) involving teams Bermuda & Netherlands in ODIs
Mukuddem has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (12) for BMUDA, going past Romaine
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (21) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
